des:
This skill will alert you with an Alexa notification whenever Virginia Governor Ralph Northam starts his daily press conference.

You can watch the Governor's conference live via his Facebook page at: https://www.facebook.com/GovernorVA/

You will also find there an archive of his past press conferences.

Note: This skill is not officilally affiliatted with Governor Northam or his office.

This skill was created and is being hosted by Witlingo. For more on witlingo, go to www.witlingo.com or send an email to contact@witlingo.com
